OME-XML utilities
=================

Overview
--------

This package provides convenience functions for OME-XML parsing and manipulation, which
have been useful in multiple pipelines.

Installation
------------

Run ``python3 -m pip install git+https://github.com/hubmapconsortium/ome-utils``.
